(how did you end up seriously injured)

273
00:15:17,240 --> 00:15:19,190
(and even your cultivation fell below the Gate of Enlightenment?)

274
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,070
(Be wary of the Great Sword Sect.)

275
00:15:21,680 --> 00:15:22,430
(My injury too)

276
00:15:22,840 --> 00:15:23,990
was their doing.

277
00:15:46,640 --> 00:15:48,230
That person is called Mak Yehae.

278
00:15:48,520 --> 00:15:49,830
He possesses the Three Divine Styles.

279
00:15:50,290 --> 00:15:52,270
The first style is the Ten Collapse Fist.

280
00:15:53,040 --> 00:15:54,870
The second is the White Wolf of Yohe.

281
00:15:56,240 --> 00:15:57,230
The final style—

282
00:15:57,600 --> 00:15:58,910
was passed down directly by the Yo Emperor.

283
00:15:59,660 --> 00:16:00,840
Its power is overwhelming.

284
00:16:01,910 --> 00:16:03,490
If I hadn't been injured,

285
00:16:03,540 --> 00:16:04,560
I could have killed him.

286
00:16:05,640 --> 00:16:07,100
How is your disciple?

287
00:16:08,640 --> 00:16:09,270
He is very strong.

288
00:16:10,320 --> 00:16:11,830
Even in the mid-stage of Spirit Mutation,

289
00:16:12,280 --> 00:16:13,750
he could stand against the Gate of Enlightenment.

290
00:16:14,560 --> 00:16:15,910
Now that his cultivation has advanced,

291
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:18,310
it's best not to provoke him carelessly.

292
00:16:19,560 --> 00:16:20,830
Since I met you,

293
00:16:21,760 --> 00:16:23,790
I've never seen you praise someone like that.

294
00:16:25,400 --> 00:16:26,830
But even so,

295
00:16:27,960 --> 00:16:29,870
he's no match for us.

296
00:16:38,040 --> 00:16:40,830
(Makbu, Cheonyo Fortress)
Even after mass slaughter,

297
00:16:41,440 --> 00:16:43,310
you're asking for a place where it won't be a problem?

298
00:16:44,360 --> 00:16:45,600
What are you planning to do?

299
00:16:52,120 --> 00:16:53,590
I've seen this technique before.

300
00:17:05,640 --> 00:17:07,230
What is this, exactly?

301
00:17:07,880 --> 00:17:09,150
It shakes the soul armor,

302
00:17:09,720 --> 00:17:11,590
and stirs the life force within the body.

303
00:17:11,960 --> 00:17:12,750
Does it shake my heart?

304
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:20,270
Even five strands of gray smoke
can disturb your mind and body.

305
00:17:21,440 --> 00:17:22,630
If you master this technique completely,

306
00:17:23,310 --> 00:17:24,950
you'll command a thousand strands of gray smoke.

307
00:17:26,040 --> 00:17:27,710
Imagine how powerful that would be.

308
00:17:32,280 --> 00:17:34,710
There is a place for slaughter—

309
00:17:35,680 --> 00:17:36,910
there is one such place.

310
00:17:38,280 --> 00:17:39,030
Hongok.

311
00:17:39,030 --> 00:17:40,040
(Hongok, Cheonyo Fortress)

312
00:17:40,040 --> 00:17:41,830
It's one of the four great prisons of the capital.

313
00:17:42,640 --> 00:17:44,430
It holds felons and those sentenced to death.

314
00:17:45,440 --> 00:17:47,270
But the security is strict,

315
00:17:47,680 --> 00:17:50,670
so I can only buy you seven days.

316
00:17:52,000 --> 00:17:53,420
Tonight at midnight,

317
00:17:53,760 --> 00:17:55,350
go to the gate of Hongok.

318
00:17:56,120 --> 00:17:57,950
Someone will guide you.

319
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:01,470
Clan Leader.

320
00:18:01,920 --> 00:18:03,030
Everything is ready.

321
00:18:03,640 --> 00:18:05,670
Wang Jang should be able to enter Hongok smoothly.

322
00:18:07,840 --> 00:18:08,230
Clan Leader.

323
00:18:09,040 --> 00:18:10,950
Hongok is a strange place.

324
00:18:11,940 --> 00:18:13,370
If Wang Jang goes in there,

325
00:18:13,800 --> 00:18:14,990
won't it be too dangerous?

326
00:18:16,240 --> 00:18:17,870
If he gains fortune,

327
00:18:18,440 --> 00:18:19,750
that is Wang's destiny.

328
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:23,430
The deputy contest is a grave matter,

329
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:25,750
so we have no choice but to take risks.

330
00:18:37,220 --> 00:18:39,420
(Hongok)

331
00:18:55,320 --> 00:18:58,470
(Heo Hoecheon, Hongok Warden, Great Circle of Spirit Mutation)
Are you the one Mak Yehae mentioned?

332
00:19:00,490 --> 00:19:01,560
Yes, I am.

333
00:19:04,160 --> 00:19:06,550
Follow me.

334
00:19:09,740 --> 00:19:15,660
(Hongok)

335
00:19:15,684 --> 00:19:47,884
