♪To see your face♪

337
00:20:05,760 --> 00:20:07,890
♪Through all the years gone by♪

338
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:11,430
♪A compass spinning in reverse♪

339
00:20:11,430 --> 00:20:13,510
♪Who decided this ending?♪

340
00:20:14,030 --> 00:20:19,080
♪Heaven erases your story♪

341
00:20:19,610 --> 00:20:25,350
♪Obsession led me on♪

342
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:28,650
♪Illusions I realized in the past♪

343
00:20:28,650 --> 00:20:30,770
♪Confusion with no truth to find♪

344
00:20:31,400 --> 00:20:34,350
♪Lost in the mire,
my original heart gone♪

345
00:20:34,350 --> 00:20:36,820
♪How can I tell right from wrong?♪

346
00:20:36,820 --> 00:20:42,230
♪Led by time,
we drift like water, all beings♪

347
00:20:42,470 --> 00:20:47,480
♪I watch as souls sink away♪

348
00:20:47,480 --> 00:20:50,500
♪I don't believe in fate set by heaven♪

349
00:20:50,500 --> 00:20:53,270
♪My soul is refined by the world♪

350
00:20:53,270 --> 00:20:56,390
♪To become immortal,
why not defy the heavens?♪

351
00:20:56,390 --> 00:20:58,940
♪Just fight back, that's enough♪

352
00:20:58,940 --> 00:21:02,130
♪In the jaws of death,
I reached the highest realm♪

353
00:21:02,130 --> 00:21:04,790
♪And learned who I truly am♪

354
00:21:04,990 --> 00:21:07,720
♪Through blood-soaked slaughter♪

355
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:10,530
♪I've never bent my will in life♪

356
00:21:10,530 --> 00:21:13,290
♪I never turn away from loneliness♪

357
00:21:13,290 --> 00:21:16,150
♪Even if pain shatters my soul♪

358
00:21:16,150 --> 00:21:19,230
♪I am reborn in hell, again and again♪

359
00:21:19,230 --> 00:21:21,800
♪And fight once more♪

360
00:21:21,800 --> 00:21:24,950
♪A place higher than the peak♪

361
00:21:24,950 --> 00:21:27,860
♪Loneliness I cannot shake♪

362
00:21:27,860 --> 00:21:30,660
♪A moth that has seen the Vermilion Bird♪

363
00:21:30,660 --> 00:21:34,270
♪Why would it fear a firefly?♪

